A mom of four has been told how she looks like her son’s younger sister after sharing a TikTok video of the family. Anna Mae Groves has left people amazed by how youthful she looks after revealing she is 46, with four adult sons. Her youthful looks mean many people have commented saying she doesn’t just look like her sons’ sister, but their younger one. Her sons’ ages range from 18, 19, 20 and 22. The video has since gone viral with over one million views and 120k likes. People were left shocked she was their mum, one wrote: “How come you look like the sister? Skincare please and makeup routine.” “Mam how old are you? Cause you look like their sister,” added another. A third commented: “You look so younggggg!” “Mam respectfully there s no way u r a mom to 4 kids and 46?” Exclaimed another. In another video, Anna shared how she keeps herself looking youthful. She revealed in a TikTok video that she uses retinol sunscreen, vitamin C and weekly AHA.” Anna shared she also has bi-monthly micro needling done, Dysport (a type of botox), and eats paleo 80% of the time. One viewer wrote: “You look so…. YOUTHFUL all around. So pretty.” This story originally appeared on The Sun and has been reproduced here with permission.